defaultQ29default 
defaultMike Gapes:default Can I take you to the fundamental economic issues? First, what is your assessment of what is happening with regard to the frameworks of fiscal responsibilities, which have been developed over the last year or so, setting out the ways in which the 
defaultOverseas
